data.description: Cute 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch style home on a large, grassy lot outside Elizabeth City. The family room features hardwood floors, a decorative accent wall and a large double window with lots of natural light. A dedicated dining area is adjacent to the family room, and just off the kitchen for ease of entertaining. The kitchen features a convenient pantry, white cabinetry accented by dark counters, and easy care vinyl floors. There is room to add a breakfast table under the double windows. A utility room off the kitchen contains the full size front loading washer and dryer and additional storage. Down the short hallway are the bedrooms. The first guest room, across from the full hall bath, sports hardwood floors, while the second guest room is carpeted and looks out to the large backyard buffered with mature trees. Just outside this bedroom is a convenient hall linen closet. The primary bedroom at the end of the hall is spacious, carpeted, and has two sets of double windows creating an open feel. A large walk-in closet with built-in shelving is one of two closets in the room. This en Suite features a large private bathroom with double sinks over a wood vanity cabinet, a separate shower, a tiled jet tub for soaking away the work day stress, and a linen closet. A large window provides natural light and a view to the backyard. The backyard is buffered by trees for privacy and features a storage building for all your toys and equipment, and the front yard looks out over acres of farmland. Set on almost an acre, this cute ranch-style home has just a few projects that need to be finished inside. Here is a tranquil home site just waiting for its new owner!
